snippet.title: 《Sdorica》 -sunset-  Global Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
《Sdorica》 -sunset- took Rayark 4 years to develop and is Rayark's first Role-playing game. A turn-based strategy game that combines story and character collection and accompanied by masterfully crafted visuals and music, we expect players to have the utmost satisfying gameplay experience. 

Sdorica-sunset- global pre-registration website: http://short.rayark.com/sdoricaPreg
